PAC urgently wanted study of implementation, effectiveness and cost-effectiveness of national MRSA screening programme. We entered into discussions with DoH who asked us to submit a formal proposal to study this. They are currently making a business case to fund it.</gtr:impact><gtr:partOfOfficialScheme>true</gtr:partOfOfficialScheme><gtr:primaryAudience>Policymakers/parliamentarians</gtr:primaryAudience><gtr:year>2008,2009</gtr:year></gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:description>National Focus meeting</gtr:description><gtr:form>A formal working group, expert panel or dialogue</gtr:form><gtr:id>C746AC20-6B50-448D-887B-036642EAC0AD</gtr:id><gtr:impact>30 infection control health care professionlals and representatives of lay organisations participated in a workshop disseminating the results of hospital visits and interveiews on isoaltion practices and preferences.

